title: Percentage of childless women , by age U.S. 2018
summary: In general Percentage of childless women has fallen over the Year.
Percentage of childless women is slightly decreasing from 20_to_24_years_old to 35_to_39_years_old.
The most drastic decrease took place within the Year 20_to_24_years_old and 25_to_29_years_old.
Maximum Percentage of childless women, about 78.6 was reported at Year 20_to_24_years_old
The lowest Percentage of childless women, of value 20.0 was reported at Year 35_to_39_years_old
